  },
  {
   "start": 17.18,
   "end": 20.3,
   "text": "Threw a bunch of it away. I forgot to film it."
  },
  {
   "start": 21.4,
   "end": 27.98,
   "text": "But yeah, dude. I got all this fucking earwax out of my ear, dude."
  },
  {
   "start": 27.98,
   "end": 33.8,
   "text": "Hopefully, I'm going to do the other ear. My ear's not any better, but maybe it will be tomorrow."
  },
  {
