  },
  {
   "start": 41.04,
   "end": 43.76,
   "text": "Big old chunk of earwax, man."
  },
  {
   "start": 44.92,
   "end": 47.94,
   "text": "And then all of this stuff. Powder."
  },
  {
   "start": 49.16,
   "end": 49.54,
   "text": "Fuck yeah."
  },
  {
   "start": 50.56,
   "end": 54.02,
   "text": "What's up, dude? By day, night by night. Not going to take my time on this one."
  },
  {
   "start": 54.1,
   "end": 57.62,
   "text": "I got to just take my time. Or I am going to take my time. Not going to speed myself."
  },
  {
   "start": 58.58,
   "end": 64.84,
   "text": "Yeah, so I got up. Went to the coffee shop for a little bit."
  },
  {
   "start": 64.9,
   "end": 66.52,
   "text": "Because that was before the library opened."
  },
  {
