   "end": 70.18,
   "text": "Finished a movie because the battery died."
  },
  {
   "start": 70.74,
   "end": 73.06,
   "text": "It wasn't Kate Beckinsale, dude. It was Rona Mitra."
  },
  {
   "start": 73.38,
   "end": 75.52,
   "text": "And Kate Beckinsale's hotter, but Rona Mitra's super hot."
  },
  {
   "start": 76.18,
   "end": 79.0,
   "text": "And then I went and had breakfast. I had another sandwich."
